216
00:22:12,066 --> 00:22:15,752
Dia akan berkata,
"Berikan aku tiga hal."

217
00:22:15,801 --> 00:22:21,301
Lalu kau berkata,
"Bola, kucing dan Roger."

218
00:22:21,873 --> 00:22:23,616
Kemudian dia...

219
00:22:23,807 --> 00:22:25,440
Dia mengarang sebuah dongeng...

220
00:22:25,442 --> 00:22:29,595
