410
00:39:15,802 --> 00:39:17,369
Aku sangat...

411
00:39:18,237 --> 00:39:19,437
Aku cukup...

412
00:39:20,539 --> 00:39:22,165
Sangat baik-baik saja.

413
00:39:29,272 --> 00:39:31,898
Baiklah, Roger.

